The paper deals with security in control systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on attacks on sensor measurements, which is a common type of attack in cyber security (cs.CR). The paper also uses mathematical tools such as linear matrix inequalities and semidefinite programs, which are commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG).
